### Core Components

- **`LoreGrep`**: Main API facade with builder pattern
- **`RepoMap`**: Fast in-memory indexes with lookup optimization  
- **`RepositoryScanner`**: File discovery with gitignore support
- **Language Analyzers**: Tree-sitter based parsing (currently Rust only)
- **Tool System**: 6 standardized tools for AI integration

### Module Structure

```
src/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ lib.rs                 # Public API exports and documentation
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ loregrep.rs           # Main LoreGrep struct and builder
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ core/                 # Core types and errors
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ types/                # Data structures (FunctionSignature, etc.)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ analyzers/            # Language-specific parsers
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ rust.rs          # Rust analyzer (tree-sitter based)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ storage/              # In-memory indexing
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ repo_map.rs      # RepoMap with fast lookups
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ scanner/              # File discovery
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ internal/             # Internal CLI and AI implementation
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cli.rs           # CLI application
